    "descriptionModule": {
      "briefSummary": "The EXActDNA-003 study will prospectively enroll participants who are planning to undergo chemotherapy for high-risk, early breast cancer, who are willing to provide tissue and blood specimens for circulating tumor DNA (ctDNA) analysis.\n\nParticipants will be followed for up to 5.5 years."
    },
